pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `account` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `username` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `password` varchar(60) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `email` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `fullName` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `phone` varchar(30) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `address` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `role` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1', PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `city` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `stateId` int(11) NOT NULL, `orderNumber` int(1) NOT NULL, `status` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '1:active 0:inactive', PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `device` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `gcm_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `ime` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `type` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=67 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `login_token` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) NOT NULL, `token` varchar(100) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `time` datetime NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=90 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `log_lat_long` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `lat` varchar(18) NOT NULL, `long` varchar(18) NOT NULL, `time` varchar(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1213 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `point_exchange` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `amount` float(13,2) DEFAULT NULL, `paymentMethod` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `point_redeem` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `amount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `payoutPaypalAddress` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `status` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `point_transfer` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `senderId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `receiverId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `amount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `request` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `passengerId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `driverId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `requestTime` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `link` varchar(3) DEFAULT NULL, `startTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `startLat` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `startLong` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `startLocation` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `endLat` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `endLong` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `endLocation` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `estimateFare` varchar(500) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=215 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `state` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `orderNumber` int(11) NOT NULL, `status` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '1:active 0:inactive', PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=57 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `transaction` ( `id` varchar(100) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `type` varchar(1) DEFAULT NULL, `amount` float(13,2) DEFAULT NULL, `action` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `destination` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `tripId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `trip` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `passengerId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `driverId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `link` varchar(3) DEFAULT NULL, `startTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `endTime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `startLat` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `startLong` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `startLocation` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `endLat` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `endLong` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `endLocation` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `distance` float(4,1) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `estimateFare` float(13,2) DEFAULT NULL, `actualFare` float(13,2) DEFAULT NULL, `driverRate` float(3,1) DEFAULT NULL, `passengerRate` float(3,1) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `need_help` int(1) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=158 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `update_pending` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `payoutPaypalAddress` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `fullName` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `carPlate` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `brand` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `model` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `year` year(4) DEFAULT NULL, `status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `document` text, `image_avt` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `image` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `image2` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `phone` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `address` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `description` text NOT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `linkType` varchar(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `user` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `fullName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `image` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `typeAccount` varchar(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `payoutPaypalAddress` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `password` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `description` text, `gender` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL, `phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `dob` date DEFAULT NULL, `address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `balance` float(13,2) DEFAULT NULL, `lat` varchar(18) DEFAULT NULL, `long` varchar(18) DEFAULT NULL, `cardNumber` varchar(30) DEFAULT NULL, `stateId` int(11) NOT NULL, `cityId` varchar(200) NOT NULL, `cvv` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL, `exp` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `isOnline` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `isActive` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `isDriver` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `token` varchar(40) DEFAULT NULL, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=54 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `user_driver` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `bankAccount` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `isOnline` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, `rate` float(3,1) DEFAULT NULL, `rateCount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `document` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `isActive` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `inactiveByAdmin` int(1) NOT NULL COMMENT '0: new driver register | 1: appove | 2 inactive', `sharedF` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `sharedG` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `linkType` varchar(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=19 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `user_passenger` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `rate` float(3,1) DEFAULT NULL, `rateCount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `sharedF` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, `sharedG` int(1) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=54 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE `vehicle` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `userId` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `carPlate` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `brand` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `model` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `year` year(4) DEFAULT NULL, `status` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `document` text, `dateCreated` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=25 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
